  "title": "Rising marital disruption in Italy and its correlates",
  "abstract": "Most of our knowledge on divorce pertains to the USA and northern Europe, while demographic studies from southern Europe are relatively scarce. Our study looks at this knowledge gap through an analysis of the correlates of marital instability in Italy.",
